title: Congratulations ALS Class 25-A > Hill Air Force Base > Article Display
text:
HILL AIR FORCE BASE â€“ Airmen enrolled in Airman Leadership School Class 25-Alpha here were honored during a graduation ceremony Dec 5. at The Landing.
ALS is a professional military education course designed to develop Airmen into effective frontline supervisors by focusing on the profession of arms, developing leadership abilities and building effective communication.
